<li><a href="/wiki/Parliamentary_and_Health_Service_Ombudsman" title="Parliamentary and Health Service Ombudsman">Health Service Ombudsman</a> - England <a href="http://www.ombudsman.org.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.ombudsman.org.uk" rel="nofollow">(Ombudsman)</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Housing_Ombudsman_Service&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Housing Ombudsman Service (page does not exist)">Housing Ombudsman Service</a> <a href="http://www.ihos.org.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.ihos.org.uk" rel="nofollow">(HOS)</a></li>
